				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">well we are in CoM getting reavers and guess who shows up, none other then rak ashirr.  the raid leader tells us all dont go near that guy. I tell him what ive been told be my fellow mages about my 56 pet. We decide to give it a try after much debate. (no one beleived me, took 2 spawns of reavers to convince them.)
<br />

<br />
Well i summon up DDD and we buff the shit out of him. the mala myself so my resist are all neg. (was told this by other mages, so that the pets resist's will take over)
<br />
Next thing i know pets health takes a huge dive. after spamming the crap out of him with heals rak is at 97%... clearly this isnt gonna work.
<br />
then pet drops, and he runs up and AE's all 23 of us to our graves.
<br />

<br />
So im left, sitting in the nexus waiting on my rez as all my guildee's say "i told you so... you just got everyone killed." &gt;&lt;
<br />

<br />
was i not supposed to debuff myself or somthing? or was this a myth to begin with?
<br />

<br />
anyway, ahd to come vent and see if it was my fault or if i forgot somthing. but i look like a total dumbass to all my guildmates now =/</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
