				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I used 49 fire pet for years on Rak, it used to work great.  Now he gets owned, so I just use epic pet and I buff up my resists over 250.  I can nearly solo Rak just healing my own epic pet.
<br />

<br />
Yeah, the pet immunities are very bugged.  It's so frustrating too.  It took years to convince guild leaders that Fire pets were the way to Kill Rak, now that they all love mage fire pets, we need to tell them it's no longer fire pets.
<br />

<br />
On our last Rak raid, my guild leader kept spamming me "KILL THE EPIC PET, CAST 49 FIRE."  I kept telling him no, just watch.  We had 2 other mages there both using 49 fire pets.  Well, sure enough, we started the Rak fight and both 49 fire died at least 4 times each.  My epic pet tanked him the whole time and lived just fine.  Had I used a 49 fire, we would have gotten owned.<br />_________________<br /><Center><bold>
